23:34.480 --> 23:36.732
- I had never heard it before.

23:36.780 --> 23:39.999
- Was there anybody new
in your father's life?

23:40.050 --> 23:41.972
Someone you met or
someone he talked about?

23:44.120 --> 23:46.088
- Abigail, he may
have been contacted

23:46.120 --> 23:48.509
